Events.RelatedBody: This makes it so when loading in VS, it will by default only load the .NET Standard/.NET Core version. Environment variables may be used to load others. This is because VS gets unstable sometimes with the default configuration. The CI builds will continue to build for all combinations and include tests for them all.
